rdf:Description.dcterms:title: Ciência Vitae controlled vocabulary - Career path
rdf:Description.dcterms:creator: FCT - Fundação para a Ciência e a Tecnologia
Hugo Festa
rdf:Description.dcterms:description: The terms in this vocabulary for the "Career path" were defined by FCT as value lists for specific attributes. From these lists, the controlled vocabulary was encoded in SKOS by Hugo Festa under the supervision of Professor Ana Alice Baptista.
